        .container.text-center
            .call-to-action
                h2 Want to sell pre-owned phones!
                a.btn.btn-default.btn-xl.wow.tada(href='#') Sell Now!
    section#contact
        .container
            .row
                .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2.text-center
                    h2.section-heading Let&apos;s Get In Touch!
                    hr.primary
                    p
                        | Ready to buy pre-owned phones? That&apos;s great. In case you have any questions, call us or write to us and we&apos;ll get back right back to you. Happy Fourfax-ing!
